dc_title_s: West Indies, Caribbean Sea, Saba, Sint Eustatius, and Saint Christopher (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From various sources to 1983." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Insets: A. West Indies, Netherlands Antilles, Saba. Scale 1:24962 -- B. West Indies, Netherlands Antilles, Sint Eustatius. Scale 1:15,000. Map No. 25607. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
